Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:10.76,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we promise not to see each other anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:14.11,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,E--Even if you say something like that now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:17.99,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem... Fine then... Just for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:22.29,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine... for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:28.29,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's going like it always does...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:39.56,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I... ATE... TOO... MUCH...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:43.58,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,This always happens at the end of every New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:46.77,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to meet Karasuma-kun during the third term like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.77,0:00:47.60,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,You're too fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:49.95,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he'll say to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:50.75,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:53.65,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Starting now, I'm going straight into a super diet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.79,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I made pizza mochi for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:02.29,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make something with fewer calories for Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:02.95,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:05.96,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal!
