Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:51.38,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Hello? Miko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.02,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The four of us on a skiing trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.36,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go! I'll go! I'll definitely go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:59.07,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going with Suou-senpai and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:04.41,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Tetsu-chan and the others were supposed to go, but they ended up catching colds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:08.77,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite the coincidence since you were saying how you needed to exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:12.50,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll burn some calories and shape up while skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:15.20,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:17.42,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:26.48,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'll be fine if I keep myself warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:33.73,Signs,Clerk,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnCentennial-Bold\bord0\shad0\pos(239,121)}Yagami
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:33.73,Signs,Clerk,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnCentennial-Bold\bord0\shad0\pos(418,120)}Stationery
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.31,SR Dialogue,Clerk,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:35.39,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.63,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I got some new screentones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.13,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,This stuff's pretty expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.25,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to use it sparingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:45.52,SR Dialogue,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,A thirty-page special appendix for the spring edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.58,SR Dialogue,Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Go draw it with your hot, passionate soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:51.56,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll draw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.17,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say you will draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:56.42,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't just appear like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.83,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stop bugging me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:04.43,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a good reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.11,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:06.89,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:10.59,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking a night bus to go on a ski trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:11.87,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.27,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma is with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:15.86,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:19.10,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,T--Tenma-chan is going skiing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:23.28,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I--I want to see her...  I want to see Tenma-chan in her magnificent skiing gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:26.91,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to go! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:30.62,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I have to finish the thirty-page special appendix for the spring edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:33.12,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, I don't have the money to go to the ski resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:37.86,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,T--The right thing to do here is to go far away and pray for Tenma-chan's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:43.19,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun for me too. {Er. We don't usually say this in English. It's like, since I'm not there, have enough fun to make up for the amount of fun I would have had there}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:46.86,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:51.10,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm back, Itoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:51.60,Signs,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAkbar\bord0\shad0\fs50\an8}Oki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:52.10,Signs,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAkbar\bord0\shad0\fs50\an8}nawa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:52.60,Signs,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAkbar\bord0\shad0\fs50\an8}Y
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.10,Signs,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAkbar\bord0\shad0\fs50\an8}a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:53.60,Signs,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAkbar\bord0\shad0\fs50\an8}y
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:58.22,SR Dialogue,Itoko,0000,0000,0000,,I went on a trip to Okinawa with Youko. We'll return in 3 days. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:02.57,SR Dialogue,Youko,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Sooki soba! I'm so excited!  Keep it up, Kenji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:05.53,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:08.62,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Man, they locked the damn door again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:11.51,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding. As if I'll make a fuss...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.49,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I am a man who learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:17.42,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Expecting something like this to happen, I secretly got a duplicate key.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:17.92,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAkbar\bord0\shad0\fs50\an8}You'll
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:18.42,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAkbar\bord0\shad0\fs50\an8}pay
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:18.92,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAkbar\bord0\shad0\fs50\an8}for
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:19.42,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAkbar\bord0\shad0\fs50\an8}this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:26.80,SR Dialogue,Itoko,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're reading this, you must have secretly made a duplicate key. You'll pay dearly for this when I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.59,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.50,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Now we have the number one competitor from the Shoutou district, Fukuda Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:38.44,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Let us watch the figure skating performance that she intends to give to win the title of "Skating Queen." {Sorta rough, TC}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.57,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! An amazingly stable Biellmann spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:47.64,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,How impressive! She's not shaking at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:53.01,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Wondeful! She's still spinning. She's still spinning! And she's {\i1}still{\i0} spinning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:57.75,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long she can continue spinning like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.72,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,I will skate this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.10,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,And she has finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:22.52,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,I will skate this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:29.26,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda exits the ring with a beautiful smile on her face. {The "Competitior" might be extraneous}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.99,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.14,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.76,SR Dialogue,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,The early morning snow feels great, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.21,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:59.90,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,It will feel even better if you wrap yourself in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.18,SR Dialogue,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,You go do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:03.48,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.71,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.67,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.16,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.94,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:37.55,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Eheh, I have to be good enough to teach Yakumo, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:41.13,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.83,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yakumo, you're such a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:49.15,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's a surprising talent in everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.36,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma, how's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:54.87,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What's wrong, Akira-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.12,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,What a weak reaction. {Stopped here}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:08:00.86,SR Dialogue,GuyA,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're great at jumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:03.58,SR Dialogue,GuyB,0000,0000,0000,,We're from the Mogul Circle in Otowadai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.54,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.12,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,It's a heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:13.13,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.05,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.16,SR Dialogue,GuyA,0000,0000,0000,,How was it? Did my feelings get through?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.97,SR Dialogue,GuyA,0000,0000,0000,,If it's okay with you... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.29,SR Dialogue,GuyB,0000,0000,0000,,The girls left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:22.94,SR Dialogue,GuyA,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:26.41,SR Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, w--wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:30.30,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Only gentlemen have a chance at flirting with us. {Err... TC, what's a good word for "ii otoko" (good man)}{Ice: I used "gentlemen"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.37,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,However, their skiing was not bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:35.26,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's too bad. Just skiing well isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:39.59,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto's current character is somewhat different from her usual character.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:42.96,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this is okay? Karasuma-kun will be shocked if he saw you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:45.48,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:49.42,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. {TC}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.70,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,K--Karasuma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:58.36,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here...? Why are you a snowman...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:01.85,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. It's quite a coincidence for us to meet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.35,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you challenging me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.48,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma's reaction was quite acute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.07,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.65,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMarkerFeltThin\bord0\shad0\1c&H7C3831&\frx36\fry4\frz349.311\pos(270,59)}Welcome to the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.65,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMarkerFeltThin\bord0\shad0\1c&H7C3831&\frx36\fry4\frz349.311\pos(289,84)}Yagami Ski Resort
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:14.11,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:23.33,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,He saw me for sure! He heard me and now he hates me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.53,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,You reap what you sow. You're at fault here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:30.84,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I only wanted to see what it was like to act like a mature woman for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:34.53,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\3c&H2F7EE0&}Like I said, you don't have to wear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:35.01,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,You're really helpless, aren't you? I'll lend you a hand just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.72,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:44.85,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we'll all jump off at the same time, and appeal to Karasuma-kun by making the characters "daisuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:48.02,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma will do the "dai" and Mikoto will do the "ki."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.21,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Will we really be able to jump that well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:52.69,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't mine the most difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:56.23,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? It's the same as the last jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:58.66,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Karasuma-kun is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:03.78,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it. {TC}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:05.44,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me, Karasuma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.47,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:12.95,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.55,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.80,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,These are my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.53,TL NOTES,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Text: You're too fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:39.06,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Note: Because Tenma dropped her hat and her poles, the words "I love you" became "You're too fat."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:34.85,SR Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}You're too fat. {Need note about this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:34.85,SR Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}You're too fat. {Need note about this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.65,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, I may be too fat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.61,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun! That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:43.50,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:46.94,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,I was vaguely aware that it was my fault for succumbing to New Year's gluttony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:49.59,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to look at my feelings this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:51.30,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, I said it was all wrong--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:54.59,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,Text: T{\alpha&HFF&}hanks
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:55.59,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,Text: Th{\alpha&HFF&}anks
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:56.59,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,Text: Tha{\alpha&HFF&}nks
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:57.59,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,Text: Than{\alpha&HFF&}ks
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.67,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,Text: Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:01.43,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:04.39,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,You're awesome, Karasuma-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:05.72,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:06.92,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:11.90,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, it's good that you're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:16.13,SR Dialogue,Harry,0000,0000,0000,,This was quite shocking. Lala suddenly said that she wanted to learn how to skate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:19.56,SR Dialogue,Tougou,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. So Lala will finally make her debut on the skating rink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.82,SR Dialogue,Errforgothername,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time skating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:28.16,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,I get to skate with Imadori-san so early in the year... Thank you, Lala-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:31.54,SR Dialogue,Tougou,0000,0000,0000,,But the memories sure come back now that I stand on top of the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:35.63,SR Dialogue,Tougou,0000,0000,0000,,The years of my youth that I spent together with the blizzards of Alaska.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:42.11,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,How does it look? Does it suit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.08,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Please change into something else right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.06,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:06.83,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,T--This... is not a sport for humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:10.75,SR Dialogue,Errforgothername,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Ah... Please don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.39,SR Dialogue,Harry,0000,0000,0000,,There you go. Loosen up a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:14.79,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:18.21,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Satsuki-chan, you're being taught by Harry-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:21.32,SR Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Ichijou-senpai looks like a professional skater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:23.66,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Hehe, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:27.13,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you doing, Lala?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:32.89,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you can't skate? I guess there's no way that a gorilla can handle human sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.89,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Imadori...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:36.65,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and teach me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.46,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:40.76,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you if you manage to come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:42.07,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:42.65,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:54.58,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,SFX: Depressed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:54.58,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally discovered your weakness, Lala. You are powerless when you're on ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.70,SR Dialogue,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:00.05,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,You really worked hard this morning, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:04.77,SR Dialogue,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,On that note, Ichijou-senpai, you're good at any sport, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:09.19,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just come here with Kousuke from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:12.16,SR Dialogue,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You were the best one on the rink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:17.06,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I tried hard, too. Why haven't I gotten any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.77,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I just found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.11,SR Dialogue,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami High School Pair Figure Skating Tournament... {I THINK hai means highschool}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.99,SR Dialogue,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it seems like this starts today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.26,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,There are some pretty extravagant prizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.46,SR Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:34.45,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,The first place winner gets a set of the newest models of a washer and dryer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.80,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll participate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:45.38,SR Dialogue,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:49.89,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I just thought... I'll go test my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:53.40,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,That's how my rival should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.17,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we'll both go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.63,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,That's some big talk coming from someone who can't even skate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:03.60,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,However, there {\i1}is{\i0} a single way for an inexperienced person like you to take first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.19,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,R--Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.93,SR Dialogue,Kousuke1,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan, where are you going? {TC}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.57,SR Dialogue,Kousuke2,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\3c&H2F7EE0&}Nee-chan, I have P.E. tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:11.18,SR Dialogue,Kousuke3,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:12.33,SR Dialogue,Kousuke4,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.13,SR Dialogue,Kousuke5,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:18.96,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,A dryer... If we had that, we wouldn't have to hang our clothes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:25.54,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,The Yagami High School Pair Figure Skating Tournament will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:28.47,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Would the pairs of competitors please gather in the rink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:33.10,Signs,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord4.5\fs32\fnFujiyama_ExtraBold-Normal\fad(500,450)\1c&HE7E6E4&\3c&HBA2B1B&\pos(323,390)}Lala & Imadori Pair
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:32.19,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Imadori, can we really win like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:34.31,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:38.61,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Dryer... Dryer... Kousuke, Onee-chan will try her best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:41.06,Signs,Tougou,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord4.5\fs32\fnFujiyama_ExtraBold-Normal\fad(600,500)\1c&HFFF5EE&\3c&HE080D8&\pos(323,390)}Karen & Tougou Pair
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:41.61,SR Dialogue,Tougou,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, let's fire up this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.48,SR Dialogue,Harry,0000,0000,0000,,How about going with me? It's still not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:48.57,SR Dialogue,Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,E--Even if you say that, I really can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:54.04,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drown you in humiliation, you gorilla-woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.66,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,First off, we have the pair of Ichijou and Tougou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:00.71,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijou gallantly skates into the rink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:02.61,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Her experience is apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.15,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,We can expect a good rating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:04.46,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:26.92,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be... Kobayashi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.69,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\3c&H2F7EE0&}Ah... I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:33.16,SR Dialogue,Kobayashi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! This is definitely the illusionary Alaska spin! {the word was illusionary, but that doesn't seem to make sense here}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:38.15,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Tougou has displayed a bold move right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:40.45,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,By himself, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:44.94,SR Dialogue,Kobayashi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good. Ichijou is left to drift around on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:47.56,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,They have completely forgotten about the "pair" part of the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.68,SR Dialogue,Ichijou,0000,0000,0000,,U--Um... Tougou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:54.64,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, the Tougou and Ichijou pair is disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:59.10,SR Dialogue,Tougou,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, it seems like an island country can't yet appreciate my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.60,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Kousuke... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.89,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Next is the pair of Lala and Imadori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:09.52,SR Dialogue,Kobayashi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of performance we can expect her, whom is from Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.83,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me, Ichijou, Tougou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:16.29,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,My appearance shall be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.74,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,It's our turn now. Let's go, Lala.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.92,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave the spectators dumbfounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:43.92,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Lala-san, that's for speed skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:46.06,SR Dialogue,Tougou,0000,0000,0000,,It's an easy mistake for beginners to make. {TC}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:55.54,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me, Imadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:59.68,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, idiot, come and get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.75,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\3c&H2F7EE0&}Stop, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:07.83,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:10.25,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you should give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:22.33,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world...? Lala has gone barefoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:26.49,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,She's also gaining a tremendous amount of speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.73,SR Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,The finishing technique looks like a gyroplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.07,SR Dialogue,Kobayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is against the rules as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:36.20,SR Dialogue,Tougou,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo, bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:40.13,SR Dialogue,Tougou,0000,0000,0000,,To tap into lucha libre for inspiration... Even I did not expect that. {lucha libre, spanish for free fight, fighters are called luchadores, took me a while to figure out}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.12,SR Dialogue,???,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.91,SR Dialogue,???,0000,0000,0000,,we headed back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:24.50,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,O--Oh crap. I lost to the kotatsu and dozed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.57,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why am I outside of the kotatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.59,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:39.54,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,My legs won't go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:42.26,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Something is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:44.10,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:53.23,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, that was... I-I-I-I-It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:56.89,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, no way... That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:58.48,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's from his point of view...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.70,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.14,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,But wait, think about this carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.92,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,His height is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.81,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:09.75,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,No... It can't happen. I mean... I mean, it's a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.79,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:17.73,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Pyo... P--P--P--P--Pyo... Are you Pyotr?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:19.78,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,W--Why, Pyotr?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:22.10,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Why the kotatsu?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.35,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:24.68,SR Dialogue,Pyotr,0000,0000,0000,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.90,SR Dialogue,Pyotr,0000,0000,0000,,An important friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:27.98,SR Dialogue,Pyotr,0000,0000,0000,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:29.81,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,"Help," you say...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:35.94,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,C--Could it be? With their sharp senses, the animals felt Tenma-chan's danger and came to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:38.90,SR Dialogue,Pyotr,0000,0000,0000,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.77,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Did she run into a snowstorm at the ski resort?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:45.73,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Or do the devilish claws of flirting guys draw near?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.77,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.46,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:55.91,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan! Stay safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.78,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:29.35,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:33.71,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I made this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.52,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,A rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:37.81,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.33,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:46.14,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,It feels nice and cool.
