Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.56,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought something like this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:25.60,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I should get going. {TC}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:28.89,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry up and continue working on my manga...
