Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:53.54,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.44,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,It feels nice and cool.
